
1. create Train records
2. create nextBookingindex = 0;
2. create Booking[] bookings
3. while.. enum -> ReservationOptions
	3.1 - New Booking
	3.2 - Cancel Booking
	3.3  - Show PNR Status/Passenger Details
	3.4 - Exit
4. 
	3.1 # New Booking -> 
		- create Booking object
		- show all trains options -> Show all trains data (train no - train name)
		- set respective fields
		- create Passenger[4]
		 	- enter all passenger records
		- add passenger array object to booking[nextBookingindex] 	
		- increment nextBookingindex++;
	3.2 -> Cancel Booking
		- Enter PNR number -> 8835831238
		- show all passenger info against above entered PNR number
		- show cancellation options 
			3.3.1 - passenger id - name 
			3.3.2 - passenger id - name
			3.3.3 - passenger id - name
			3.3.4 - passenger id - name
			3.3.5 - all	
	3.3 # Show PNR ->
		- Enter PNR number -> 8835831238
5. Repeat step 3
6. 3.4 # Exit -> program stop
													